title: Ask HN: Are technical interviews changing in response to ChatGPT?
Show HN: ScribbleToArt, Turn any scribbles into art with Stable Defussion
text:
Hello Hacker News community!

I'm excited to share a tool that I've recently built called ScribbleToArt. It's a tool that can transform any scribbles/outlines into stunning artwork in just seconds. With ScribbleToArt, you can choose from a variety of pre-defined styles, making it easy to create beautiful masterpieces that are unique to your style. No more prompt engineering needed.

ScribbleToArt is powered by Stable Deffusion(ControlNet) model

I built this tool with a lot of passion and dedication, and I'd love for you to try it out and provide your valuable feedback. I'm looking forward to hearing your thoughts!

Thank you for your time and support!"
